title: Red Dead Redemption for iPhone is SO Good

author: Austin Evans
description:
Valve announced the Steam Machine but won't tell us how much it costs...and I think I know why. There's a massive memory crisis hitting the entire tech industry right now that most people don't understand. If you're planning to buy a PS5, Switch 2 or gaming PC in 2025 or 2026, you need to watch this.
